<h3 id="多帧滑动窗口与后退n帧协议gbn">多帧滑动窗口与后退N帧协议(GBN)</h3>
<p><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/10/06PWSP.png" alt="06PWSP.png" loading="lazy"><br>
<img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/10/06iKkd.png" alt="06iKkd.png" loading="lazy"><br>
<img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/10/06Fy8I.png" alt="06Fy8I.png" loading="lazy"><br>
<img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/10/06kuRI.png" alt="06kuRI.png" loading="lazy"><br>
