<h3 id="多帧滑动窗口与选择重传协议sr">多帧滑动窗口与选择重传协议(SR)</h3>
<p><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/10/06VZoF.png" alt="06VZoF.png" loading="lazy"><br>
<img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/10/06eJ8H.png" alt="06eJ8H.png" loading="lazy"><br>
