<h2 id="介质访问控制">介质访问控制</h2>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="3"><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/11/0g89S0.png" alt="0g89S0.png" loading="lazy"></figure>
<h3 id="信道划分介质访问控制">信道划分介质访问控制</h3>
<ol>
<li>FDM</li>
<li>TDM
<ol>
<li>注意STDM,使用集中器</li>
</ol>
</li>
<li>WDM</li>
<li>CDM</li>
</ol>
<h3 id="随机访问介质访问控制">随机访问介质访问控制</h3>
<h4 id="aloha协议">ALOHA协议</h4>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="4"><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/11/0gUBn0.png" alt="0gUBn0.png" loading="lazy"></figure>
<h4 id="csma协议carrier-sense-multiple-access载波侦听多路访问">CSMA协议(Carrier Sense Multiple Access,载波侦听多路访问)</h4>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="5"><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/11/0gakgs.png" alt="0gakgs.png" loading="lazy"></figure>
<ol>
<li>1-坚持CSMA<br>
<img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/11/0gaJDx.png" alt="0gaJDx.png" loading="lazy"></li>
<li>非坚持CSMA<br>
<img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/11/0gy4u4.png" alt="0gy4u4.png" loading="lazy"></li>
<li>p-坚持CSMA<br>
<img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/11/0gyetx.png" alt="0gyetx.png" loading="lazy"><br>
缺点:冲突了还是会把数据发完,造成浪费</li>
<li>对比<br>
<img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/11/0g6C5t.png" alt="0g6C5t.png" loading="lazy"></li>
</ol>
<h4 id="csmacdcollision-detection">CSMA/CD(Collision Detection)</h4>
<p><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/11/0gcGfP.png" alt="0gcGfP.png" loading="lazy"><br>
<img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/12/0RUEkT.png" alt="0RUEkT.png" loading="lazy"><br>
书上的图只是为了得到2τ,CSMA/CD的根本目的为了在传输完成前就可以检测到碰撞进而停止发送,而不是让他们发送出去之后检测到碰撞<br>
<img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/12/0Rw4HI.png" alt="0Rw4HI.png" loading="lazy"><br>
<img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/12/0R0mUx.png" alt="0R0mUx.png" loading="lazy"><br>
<img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/12/0R03KH.png" alt="0R03KH.png" loading="lazy"></p>
<h4 id="csmacacollision-avoidance">CSMA/CA(Collision Avoidance)</h4>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="6"><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/12/0Rs4t1.png" alt="0Rs4t1.png" loading="lazy"></figure>
<h3 id="轮询访问介质访问控制令牌传递协议">轮询访问介质访问控制:令牌传递协议</h3>
<p><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/12/0R2YZD.png" alt="0R2YZD.png" loading="lazy"><br>
<img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/12/0RWoaF.png" alt="0RWoaF.png" loading="lazy"></p>
